@startuml

/'
Activity Diagram – Extended Control Structures

Purpose:
Demonstrates loops, parallel processing, and annotations to explain
more complex logic.

*Elements:
- repeat/backward: Loop structure
- switch/case: Multiple conditional branches
- note: Explanatory text for steps
'/

start
repeat
  :Enter Credentials;
  note left: User has 3 attempts
backward:Increment Attempt Count;
repeat while (Valid?) is (no) not (yes)

switch (User Role?)
case ( Admin )
  :Redirect to Admin Panel;
case ( Moderator )
  :Redirect to Audit Log;
case ( User )
  :Redirect to Dashboard;
endswitch

stop

@enduml
